public class ShipmentLinkedList
extends java.lang.Object

Maintains all of the Shipments of the VRP. Title: ShipmentLinkedList Description: This class maintains all of the Shipments of the VRP. Further information about each of the shipments is stored in the Shipment class. Copyright: Copyright (c) 2003
